ezvcard.io.xml

Class XCardReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • ezvcard.io.xml.XCardReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class XCardReader
extends Object
implements Closeable

    Reads xCards (XML-encoded vCards) in a streaming fashion.

    Example: 

     File file = new File("vcards.xml");
 List<VCard> vcards = new ArrayList<VCard>();
 XCardReader xcardReader = new XCardReader(file);
 VCard vcard;
 while ((vcard = xcardReader.readNext()) != null) {
        vcards.add(vcard);
 }
 xcardReader.close();

    Author:
    Michael Angstadt
    See Also:
    RFC 6351
